snippet.title: 25 Best Acting Performances of 2025 Video Games
snippet.description:
In this video we showcase the 25 best video game acting performances of the year, presented in no particular order. Amazing performances from the likes of Jennifer English , Ben Starr, Troy Baker and more! Some spoilers ahead for games like Ghost of Yotei, Clair Obscur: Expedition 33, Death Stranding 2, Dispatch and more.
